au.org.theark.gdmi.util
Class GWASImport

java.lang.Object
  au.org.theark.gdmi.util.GWASImport

public class GWASImport
extends java.lang.Object

GWASImport provides support for importing PLINK compatible ped and map files. It features state-machine behaviour to allow an external class to deal with how to store the data pulled out of the files.

Author:
elam

public void processMap(java.lang.String mapFilePath)
                throws java.io.IOException,
                       java.lang.OutOfMemoryError
Imports the PLINK compatible map file. Default map file format assumed (i.e. 4 columns) as per: http://pngu.mgh.harvard.edu/~purcell/plink/data.shtml#map
